						               													<description>Vereimejate Kants - K&amp;otilde;ige k&amp;otilde;hedam lauam&amp;auml;ng  (Bloodsuckers castle - the creepiest board game)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A population of humans are in danger. Behind the gray walls of the big castle, a clan of bloodsucking vampires have been living for centuries. The monsters and their evil master Thanateros have been terrorizing people for a long time and they have had enough of deaths and horror. Four bravest warriors will lead their soldiers to end vampires reign with superior &amp;quot;Speed&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Accuracy&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;Strength&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;To get to the castle they first have to go through a dark forest where they have to fight with werewolves, zombies, forest vampires. In the castle real challenge awaits, there are vampires that have powers that no man can match. Unless the warriors find the amulets that make them worthy. By killing weaker enemies, player can collect amulets, what they need in order to enter the castle. 5 similar is required. Extra powers will be given to player when he collects the amulets.He can use second-level heroes, which are coming out from the &amp;quot;treasure&amp;quot; deck. As will be other cards that give bonuses or will ruin you. &amp;#10;Player are using dice to move and actioncards to fight the monsters.&amp;#10;Player can enter the castle when the amulets are collected. There player needs to fight even stronger vampires and after many fights, he needs to reach the master vampire Thanateros, which will be the final battle. &amp;#10;After victory, final move will be to roll the dice and see what happens to you in the future...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
